Canadian pop sensation Justin Bieber is set to accompany Floyd Mayweather into his $300million Las Vegas mega-fight with Manny Pacquiao.

The duo have been close friends for years and the 21-year-old performer has accompanied 'Money' into the ring on numerous occasions.

He even joined the fighter on stage during a recent press conference ahead of the May 2 fight. 

